### Description of Issue/Question
This used to work but now fails when there are non ASCII characters in the paths

```
## manage config
dlmgr.sabnzbd.config::directories:
  file.directory:
    - name: /data/sabnzbd
    - user: sabnzbd
    - group: dlbox_rw
    - makedirs: True
    - mode: 0750
    - file_mode: 0640
    - recurse:
        - user
        - group
        - mode
    - require:
        - dlmgr.sabnzbd::package
```

